Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.42,0:00:10.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要下船 让我下船
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.39,0:00:14.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出来了 就要出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.76,0:00:17.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我振作些 浓眉老师
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.91,0:00:20.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凯晕船了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.72,0:00:24.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的大浪确实扛不住啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.91,0:00:27.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也有些…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.15,0:00:29.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.86,0:00:33.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快…让船不要摇了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.98,0:00:40.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晕船而已嘛 真是没用
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.98,0:00:44.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话虽如此 但这样晃真扛不住啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.13,0:00:48.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先找个地方休息 等天气好转吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.79,0:00:49.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.55,0:00:53.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然和预定的航线有些偏离
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.70,0:00:56.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但东边应该有座小岛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.18,0:00:57.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么一说我倒想起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.27,0:01:00.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中立海域的无人岛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.44,0:01:03.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个…对 是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.96,0:01:08.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就去这儿吧 去避避…吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.05,0:01:12.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来不及了 赶紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.14,0:01:15.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,转舵 向东北方航向
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.37,0:01:17.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.57,0:03:15.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,振作点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.27,0:03:17.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是鸣人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.26,0:03:21.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边 这边
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.80,0:03:24.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们怎么来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.85,0:03:26.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小樱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.68,0:03:30.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,浪确实很大
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.95,0:03:33.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相当厉害啊 大家都要吐了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.23,0:03:37.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了让凯老师稍事休息 所以才来这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.06,0:03:43.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们又执行什么任务呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.22,0:03:46.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实是根据纲手大人的指示
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.96,0:03:50.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们去东海？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.76,0:03:53.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第四次忍界大战很快就要开战
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.45,0:03:57.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那之前
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.85,0:04:00.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,需要准备充足的秘药以及兵粮丸的材料
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.10,0:04:03.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.57,0:04:04.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七草岛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.42,0:04:07.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是药草的宝库
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.34,0:04:11.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地图上标有药草所在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.75,0:04:16.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曼陀罗草 活力人参 红蝾螈 大蔓藤
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.86,0:04:18.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是什么都有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.15,0:04:20.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…这里是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.02,0:04:23.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如有余力去看看也行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.95,0:04:24.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,切不可勉强
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.75,0:04:30.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以小樱就成了队长
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.86,0:04:33.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凯老师睡着了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.39,0:04:35.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,万事准备就绪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.66,0:04:37.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随时随地可以出发
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.42,0:04:40.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少了鹿丸的十班残余啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.06,0:04:42.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不是残余呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.55,0:04:44.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该是多余的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.64,0:04:48.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们七班不也是少了鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.54,0:04:50.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是各做各的去了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.28,0:04:53.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐井应该也去执行其他任务了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.05,0:04:57.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.28,0:04:59.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都有自己的任务啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.02,0:05:02.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我什么都不用做没关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.68,0:05:06.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来有很重大的任务等着鸣人去完成
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.21,0:05:09.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次出航也是为了这个目的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.45,0:05:12.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.26,0:05:13.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.53,0:05:16.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正也要等凯老师恢复后才能出航
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.97,0:05:19.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不如帮帮我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.66,0:05:21.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,采药草吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.10,0:05:25.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正是 采草而已 游刃有余吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.65,0:05:28.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对 都多少次了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.92,0:05:30.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那这个呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.02,0:05:33.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底在看什么呢 完全不对嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.70,0:05:37.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经完全摸不清头脑了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.13,0:05:39.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一点都不简单啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.00,0:05:43.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不如和他们两人一起照看凯老师的好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.38,0:05:46.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想等凯先生恢复后
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.34,0:05:49.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,商讨一下航海日程
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.03,0:05:53.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了 留下也没啥事做
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.73,0:05:55.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给 以这个作参考吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.46,0:05:58.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦战争开始的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.19,0:05:59.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必定会有伤者出现
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.07,0:06:01.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,数百人…数千人…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.26,0:06:04.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了治疗那些伤员
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.26,0:06:06.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是绝对要完成的任务
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.91,0:06:15.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纲手大人明明说这里是药草的宝库
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.99,0:06:18.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比想象中的难找啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.40,0:06:20.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不要换个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.36,0:06:22.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,往更高处走走看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.06,0:06:25.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还得找兵粮丸的材料
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.79,0:06:26.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.92,0:06:28.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样完全不够
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.90,0:06:31.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍等
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.97,0:06:36.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.82,0:06:38.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好 记住味道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.28,0:06:44.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好 干活
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.62,0:06:45.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.03,0:06:47.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个吗…不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.28,0:06:48.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个吧…不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.74,0:06:50.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个吗…不对…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.61,0:06:52.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该是这个了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.62,0:06:59.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这味道好像不太一样 又好像有点相似
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.63,0:07:01.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真奇怪 这种地方的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.09,0:07:05.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该会生长着曼陀罗草的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.26,0:07:07.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是气候起变化了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.02,0:07:10.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是活力人参
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.86,0:07:13.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛 还是有的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.08,0:07:14.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长了一堆呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.41,0:07:17.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能做出很不错的兵粮丸呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.37,0:07:19.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先等等
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.16,0:07:21.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.84,0:07:27.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失敬了 那边的活力人参是我们先发现的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.21,0:07:32.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个护额 看来是木叶的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.70,0:07:35.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.46,0:07:41.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大国之人是不会在意我们这些小国的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.75,0:07:48.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们乃南边红州岛的忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.89,0:07:51.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是上忍 坂东
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.04,0:07:52.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下忍 佐田
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.55,0:07:53.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是木地
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.45,0:07:55.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,传言战争临近
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.75,0:07:58.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,便前来这座小岛收集药草
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.99,0:08:04.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛 难怪怎么找都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.07,0:08:07.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因为你们捷足先登了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.10,0:08:10.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 已经收集一大部分了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.42,0:08:13.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是这样一来你们就该苦恼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.90,0:08:14.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.86,0:08:21.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个是…感激不尽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.00,0:08:23.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是帮了忍者联军的大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.78,0:08:25.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们满意吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.37,0:08:28.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么就…好的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.09,0:08:36.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我算 我算 我算算算…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.08,0:08:40.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一束这个价位如何
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.50,0:08:41.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.38,0:08:45.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,木叶的人真不好商量啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.79,0:08:49.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么就让我好好学习学习…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.24,0:08:50.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样一来怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.77,0:08:52.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然要收钱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.63,0:08:54.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是送给我们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.31,0:08:58.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,饶了小的们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.56,0:08:59.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.97,0:09:03.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们这样的小国是生存不下去的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.71,0:09:07.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了 木叶若不愿意购买的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.61,0:09:11.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就指望其他村里的大名殿下们出资了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.47,0:09:15.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战争中会受伤的不只是忍者啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.61,0:09:18.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…明知道如此还做买卖吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.81,0:09:22.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们不也是靠任务赚钱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.72,0:09:25.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,分出级别 标上价钱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.47,0:09:31.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失礼了…无论如何敬请谅解
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.21,0:09:35.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也需要挣回自我防御的资金
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.87,0:09:36.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.06,0:09:37.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.57,0:09:41.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拔一株为了钱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.20,0:09:42.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿哟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.01,0:09:46.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拔两株为了钱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.40,0:09:47.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.28,0:09:50.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拔三株为了钱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.85,0:09:51.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿哟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.91,0:09:54.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拔四株为了钱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.06,0:09:55.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.13,0:09:56.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.61,0:09:58.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样一来就无法完成任务了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.78,0:10:03.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话是这样说 又不能半路抢劫他们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.18,0:10:06.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是当然 都组成忍者联军了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.60,0:10:09.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能和其他村子的忍者发生纠纷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.56,0:10:12.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛 没啥好苦恼的 小樱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.45,0:10:16.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这座岛是药草的宝库对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.43,0:10:18.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说这附近被他们抢先了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.53,0:10:20.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也没啥了不起的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.80,0:10:22.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您所说极是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.63,0:10:25.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来才是珍稀物品
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.61,0:10:28.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只不过不是那么容易采集到的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.02,0:10:32.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实有个棘手的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.64,0:10:34.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就交给我了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.82,0:10:39.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.85,0:10:41.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么暂且告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.71,0:10:43.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请多加小心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.75,0:10:53.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 走掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.38,0:10:55.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.52,0:10:57.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肚子…好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.98,0:11:02.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃了药草为何肚子会疼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.98,0:11:04.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,药草
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.33,0:11:07.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你该不会是误吃了毒草吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.67,0:11:20.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人 快点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.94,0:11:23.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说是这么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.05,0:11:27.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这附近应该长着大蔓藤才是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.30,0:11:30.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经被采掉了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.07,0:11:32.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但愿不是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.96,0:11:34.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.37,0:11:41.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赶快 再慢点什么都没了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.64,0:11:46.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大蔓藤的花
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.65,0:11:49.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是还留着一些嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.46,0:11:52.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛 那些家伙不是给我们留了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.03,0:11:54.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就赶紧…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.00,0:11:55.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.64,0:11:56.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.79,0:11:58.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,留下的是为了播种
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.08,0:12:01.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,采草不除根是采药草的原则
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.79,0:12:05.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊 不是为了我们留的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.47,0:12:06.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去下一个吧 下一个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.89,0:12:09.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去河流上游找红蝾螈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.00,0:12:10.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赶快
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.27,0:12:15.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.02,0:12:17.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是他们 果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.59,0:12:20.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等着
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.14,0:12:22.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 写着什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.85,0:12:26.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勿过此桥 红州专用
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.92,0:12:29.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说什么不要过桥 我就过给你看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.83,0:12:30.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.75,0:12:32.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞不好是陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.58,0:12:36.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事没事 肚子也好多了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.04,0:12:40.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身体…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.09,0:12:44.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身体麻痹得动弹不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.82,0:12:46.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.67,0:12:50.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这卷起的不是麻痹草吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.34,0:12:53.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是个圈套 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.73,0:12:54.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个…但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.02,0:13:00.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别管那个了…救…救命…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.32,0:13:04.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.25,0:13:14.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那边情况如何
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.08,0:13:16.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是找不到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.52,0:13:26.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到红蝾螈了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.67,0:13:33.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了 红蝾螈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.59,0:13:36.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来就这么一只
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.09,0:13:39.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这尺寸不过是个娃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.06,0:13:41.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能放生了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.92,0:13:43.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又被算计了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.90,0:13:46.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都怪时间被平白无故地浪费了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.45,0:13:49.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是啊 怎能这么悠哉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.60,0:13:52.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好冷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.33,0:13:54.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赶紧去下一个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.70,0:13:58.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得是谁让我们这么悠闲的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.30,0:14:01.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.06,0:14:03.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里已经没戏了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.53,0:14:05.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.16,0:14:09.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样一来 只能去这里了 地狱谷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.63,0:14:10.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地狱谷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.27,0:14:13.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从地底涌出的泥沼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.46,0:14:17.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是能治疗撞伤 刀伤 扭伤等等的万能泥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.07,0:14:19.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是纲手大人她…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.72,0:14:22.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里若有余力去看看也行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.16,0:14:24.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,切不可勉强
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.93,0:14:28.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,估计是相当危险的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.56,0:14:30.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.43,0:14:34.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就去地狱谷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.53,0:14:48.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该怎么做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.23,0:14:50.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.26,0:14:53.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们别老是做偷鸡摸狗的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.95,0:14:56.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不 怎么会呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.69,0:14:59.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎能对木叶的各位做那样的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.31,0:15:03.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是做采集药草的准备罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.27,0:15:06.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不跟你们一般见识
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.35,0:15:08.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿到万能泥浆就回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.55,0:15:09.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.05,0:15:11.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 又想拖住我们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.31,0:15:14.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是无偿服务
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.58,0:15:15.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.11,0:15:21.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瓦斯会时不时地喷出来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.75,0:15:25.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是毒气 长时间接触的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.33,0:15:28.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且是无规则的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.82,0:15:33.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要怎样才能得到深处的万能泥浆呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.76,0:15:35.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多重影分身之术
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.55,0:15:38.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.62,0:15:42.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.82,0:15:47.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好烫
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.91,0:15:51.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.96,0:15:58.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好 万能泥浆 我拿走了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.73,0:16:05.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好烫  没工具拿不走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.64,0:16:12.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这真是个大赌博啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.71,0:16:14.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能碰运气了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.20,0:16:16.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这根本就行不通啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.48,0:16:19.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多亏您 总算确认好路线了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.20,0:16:21.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打算去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.60,0:16:25.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我做生意可不是抱着玩玩的态度
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.30,0:16:28.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了小国的生存 我们也得拼死努力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.38,0:16:31.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等瓦斯消失后就上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.86,0:16:32.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.51,0:16:36.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁现在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.40,0:16:56.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.45,0:16:57.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,危险
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.71,0:17:00.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风遁.大突破
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.38,0:17:08.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风遁之术 挺能干的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.32,0:17:15.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.63,0:17:18.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做得好 撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.49,0:17:19.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.98,0:17:25.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.40,0:17:40.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风遁.大突破
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.38,0:17:42.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赶快
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.32,0:17:46.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快跑 快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.71,0:17:48.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.79,0:17:51.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光跑来不及的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.37,0:17:57.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风遁.大…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.97,0:18:01.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续跑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.63,0:18:02.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.70,0:18:11.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用你们帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.30,0:18:15.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欠下大国的情 之后不知道要赔多少钱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.30,0:18:18.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会要钱的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.37,0:18:22.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不信
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.72,0:18:25.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们一直对我们小国…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.03,0:18:28.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都说这是无偿服务了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.90,0:18:32.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大玉螺旋丸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.65,0:18:54.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 该怎么说呢 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.15,0:18:58.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感谢你救了我们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.77,0:19:03.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 真的不收钱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.89,0:19:06.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我早说是免费的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.79,0:19:10.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是他国的忍者 也不全是敌对的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.99,0:19:12.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.46,0:19:15.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有时候也突破利益关系携手合作
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.21,0:19:18.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在的忍者联军就是这样的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.94,0:19:20.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 这样的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.35,0:19:23.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐田 木地
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.01,0:19:25.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像真是免费的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.60,0:19:27.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怀着感恩的心来接受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.29,0:19:36.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是来自我们的免费服务
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.17,0:19:39.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请收下这万能泥浆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.73,0:19:41.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以吗 谢谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.07,0:19:45.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然 如果可以的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.32,0:19:49.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那边所有已经采集好的药草也请收下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.81,0:19:54.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就算我们送给忍者联军的礼物吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.42,0:19:57.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 任务完成啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.76,0:19:59.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.90,0:20:01.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.68,0:20:03.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你太厉害了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.51,0:20:08.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不 你才是 今天深受启发了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.56,0:20:21.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢 你们也加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.84,0:20:27.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过这样合适吗 坂东大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.56,0:20:29.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,免费给他们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.68,0:20:34.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁现在给联军一个恩惠
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.37,0:20:37.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃点小亏就能得到好处
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.27,0:20:44.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再会了 大地
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.57,0:20:46.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暂时的离别
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.37,0:20:50.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多亏了你 我的身体已经能适应船了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.47,0:20:52.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真希望是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.05,0:21:02.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人 加油啊 特别任务加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.24,0:22:52.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在浓雾弥漫的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.49,0:22:54.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听说那个就会出现
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.93,0:22:59.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是引导死者灵魂的 在乌鸦的指引之下出现
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.01,0:23:04.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若隐若现的巨大鬼火就是它的象征
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.45,0:23:06.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遇到就意味着终结
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.68,0:23:09.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就将踏上前往死者国度的航行
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.94,0:23:13.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下集的火影疾风传是 被诅咒的幽灵船
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.22,0:23:16.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 出现了！
